We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

(a) To provide, maintain, and improve our Service;
(b) To process transactions and send related information;
(c) To send you technical notices, updates, security alerts, and administrative messages;
(d) To respond to your comments, questions, and customer service requests;
(e) To communicate with you about products, services, offers, and events;
(f) To monitor and analyze trends, usage, and activities in connection with our Service;
(g) To detect, investigate, and prevent fraudulent transactions and other illegal activities;
(h) To comply with legal obligations.

We may share your information in the following circumstances:

(a) With service providers who perform services on our behalf, subject to confidentiality obligations;
(b) In response to a request for information if we believe disclosure is required by applicable law, regulation, or legal process;
(c) If we believe your actions are inconsistent with our user agreements or policies, or to protect the rights, property, and safety of us or others;
(d) In connection with, or during negotiations of, any merger, sale of company assets, financing, or acquisition;
(e) With your consent or at your direction.

We do not sell your personal information to third parties.

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

